high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink.
Pick up the black cup from the sink.
Carry the cup and turn to the right, to find the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup inside. Shut the door, then open it again and take the cup out. Shut the door.
Carry the cup and turn to the left, and face the sink on the left.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a cup and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed to sink directly across the room.
Pick up black mug from center of sink, to the right of the green sponge.
Turn right, proceed to counter with microwave.
Open microwave, put mug in back of microwave, to the right of the back egg, close door.  Wait three seconds, open microwave door,  remove mug, shut microwave door.
Turn left, proceed to sink, turn right to face sink.
Place mug in bottom right corner of sink.
anns.task_desc: Pick up mug, heat in microwave, put into sink.

high_descs: Pick up the black mug from the sink
Put the mug in the microwave and heat it
Put the heated mug in the sink
anns.task_desc: Take a mug, heat it, and put it back
